headline: Bestow Appoints Insurance Veteran Cindy DeArmond as Chief Revenue Officer
summary: Bestow, a leading insurance technology platform, today announced the appointment of Cindy DeArmond as Chief Revenue Officer, reinforcing the company's commitment to accelerating growth and digital transformation across the life insurance industry.
